I'm a Certified Personal Trainer and Content Marketing Writer who specializes in health and fitness. I love writing blogs, articles, and guides that cover topics in the health and fitness vertical. 

You can check out my website and portfolio here: <https://www.crescitanna.com|https://www.crescitanna.com>

If you're looking for a writer or know of anyone looking for a writer in the health and fitness space, please send me a DM.

Thank you:blush:

Hello all! My name is Jamie Vassar and I am a freelance writer predominately, but not limited to, writing about customer success tools and teams for B2B and SaaS companies. I have previously written for Nicereply, Help Scout, Lumoa, and Qwilr and would love to take on new clients if anyone is looking.

Thank you so much for your time.
